originalText.text: We've been working with West 47 Accounting since 2015 and the results have been great. I manage a Gabriela Wakeham Floral Design in the Chelsea-Midtown area and finding Julia and her team has been a great help to us. They are knowledgeable, efficient, and respond quickly when we call. We've several times asked them to clean up our books with tight deadlines at tax time -- and they're always able to finish what we need. Based on our experience, West 47 Accounting  is the best bookkeeper Midtown has to offer. We've already recommended them to several other businesses in our area and will continue doing so.

originalText.text: West 47 Accounting has been handling the bookkeeping of my business for the past 5 years.  Bookkeeping and Accounting is a critical aspect of our business - a leading digital agency with Fortune 500 clients. Julia the owner is the best bookkeeper I have worked with over the past 18 years. Our CPA firm has no issues with our books.  She is an expert with Quickbooks.  She is very accurate, thorough, professional, and works 2x faster than any Bookkeeper I have employed.  I highly recommend West 47 Accounting for your booking needs.
